citations.desc: Access and inspection of records and property; submission of itineraries.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 10:47-11:17am on
2/4/2021. The inspector honked her horn and called the number on file. The number on file was non-working, no
message was able to be left. Inspector waited 30 minutes at the facility prior to departing.
End Section

Access and inspection of records and property; submission  of itineraries. 
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 10:47-11:17am on

message was able to be left.  Inspector waited 30 minutes at the facility prior to departing.
